sentences: Derrick Lee Murdock (aka "Dock," born December 13, 1957 in Philadelphia) is an American Bassist, Composer and Producer.
He is best known as the former house bassist on The Tonight Show with Jay Leno  led by Musical Conductor Kevin Eubanks on The Tonight Show with Jay Leno   from (2006–2011).
